    'SysVarFilterSetNamespacePassOnChange': 'Syntax: long sysVarFilterSetNamespacePassOnChange (char[] namespace, char[] filterName); // form 1 long sysVarFilterSetNamespacePassOnChange (char[] namespace); // form 2\nDescription: Sets namespace of the filter to mode: Pass on change .\nParameters: filterName Name of the specific filter. namspace Namespace which should be filtered.\nReturns: Return&#160;Values 0 No error, function successful. 1 Namespace was not found or second try to define the same namespace. 2 Variable was not found or second try to define the same variable. 3 No writing right for the namespace available. 4 Variable h',
    'SysVarFilterSetNamespacePassOnUpdate': 'Syntax: long sysVarFilterSetNamespacePassOnUpdate (char[] namespace, char[] filterName); // form 1 long sysVarFilterSetNamespacePassOnUpdate (char[] namespace); // form 2\nDescription: Sets default state of the filter to mode: Pass on update .\nParameters: filterName Name of the specific filter. namspace Namespace which should be filtered.\nReturns: Return&#160;Values 0 No error, function successful. 1 Namespace was not found or second try to define the same namespace. 2 Variable was not found or second try to define the same variable. 3 No writing right for the namespace available. 4 Variable h',
