    'cclProvidedEventSetSubscriptionStateIsolated': 'Syntax: int32_t cclProvidedEventSetSubscriptionStateIsolated(cclProvidedEventID providedEventID, bool subscribed);\nDescription: Sets the low level subscription state of a provider side service event port.\nParameters: providedEventID The ID of a provider side service event port (returned by cclProvidedEventGetID function). subscribed If this parameter is set to true, the event port will transition to state CCL_SUBSCRIPTION_STATE_SUBSCRIBED, otherwise it will trans\nReturns: Return&#160;Values CCL_SUCCESS The subscription state was successfully changed. CCL_WRONGSTATE The function may only be cal',
